_sText:
In the middle of the map you will notice ten glass cells. These are made specifically for last reaction, trivia, or any other game that causes the last person to react/answer to die. There is a button on the wall of each cell, when the button is pressed, the floor of the cell breaks causing the person inside to fall into "hell". The floor will only break once the door of the glass cell has been opened.



This map is not to be edited. Please do not copy things out of this level and implement them into yours. You may decompile this map only to see how certain things were done.
